author: Tommy Wilkes
title: Dollar cements rebound after jobs data triggers tapering bets - Reuters
description: The dollar hit a four-month high against the euro on Monday, reversing a recent fall after strong labour market data encouraged investors to bring forward their bets on the Federal Reserve reducing its pandemic-era stimulus.
